             Below is the JSON schema for the request and response payloads, as well as samples showing how to format these payloads in .NET.

             Additional information can be found in the Purview service REST API documentation: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/rest/api/purview/


             This method takes a one of the scan types below as a payload. Please select a scan type to view the schema for this type.
